                <p class="pb-2">Our plugins are easy to install. Simply download the JAR file, place it in your server's plugins folder, and restart your server. Detailed installation instructions are provided in the documentation for each plugin.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-dark-base/70 rounded-lg p-4 shadow-md border border-primary-800/20 hover:border-primary-700/30 transition-all duration-300 group/faq relative overflow-hidden faq-item">
              <!-- Subtle glow on hover -->
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600/0 via-primary-500/5 to-primary-600/0 opacity-0 group-hover/faq:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
